PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781894898
OL,3,CBurnham confirms he won't accept a
OL,4,Ccabinet job in Starmer's government
OL,6,FDespite warning against any leadership
OL,7,Fbattles, Starmer went on to say that
OL,8,Fhe will not walk away from a
OL,9,Fleadership contest if one is called.
OL,11,FHe said: "if there is a challenge,
OL,12,Fthen I intend to fight".
OL,14,FUnder Labour party rules, any
OL,15,Fchallenger must gather public support
OL,16,Ffrom at least 81 MPs but the current
OL,17,Fleader does not need this and can
OL,18,Fstand regardless.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
