OL,3,CBurnham confirms he won't accept a
OL,4,Ccabinet job in Starmer's government
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FWes Streeting has repeatedly said he
OL,12,Fhas the required backing from MPs and
OL,13,Fhas indicated he would trigger a
OL,14,Fleadership context as early as next
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,FThis comes on the final day of the G7
OL,18,Fsummit where Starmer has been meeting
OL,19,Fwith world leaders to discuss Ukraine
OL,20,Fand Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
