OL,3,CBurnham confirms he won't accept a
OL,4,Ccabinet job in Starmer's government
OL,6,FThe pressure has been mounting on the
OL,7,Fprime minister in terms of defence
OL,8,Fspending after the shock resignation
OL,9,Fof his Defence Secretary, John Healey
OL,10,Fon Thursday.
OL,12,FStarmer told ITV News' Political
OL,13,FEditor Robert Peston that he
OL,14,F"disagrees" with Healey that the
OL,15,Fcurrent military spending plans are
OL,16,Fnot enough.
OL,18,FHe also said that Trump's Iran deal
OL,19,Fwas a "good thing".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
